# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  config.js is gitignored by default
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# config.js holds your InfluxDB token, your host and your entity IDs.
# It is ignored here on purpose — commit config.example.js instead.
#
# This is a default, not a guarantee: `git add -f config.js` will still
# stage it, and a rule added after the fact does not remove a secret that
# is already in your history. Check `git status` before you commit.
config.js

# Kiosk browser profile (created at runtime)
_kiosk-profile/

# Logs
*.log
logs/

# Node
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# Local snapshots / backups
_restore/
*.bak
*.bak[0-9]
